
Trying to find out what to do with those out-of-town guests for Thanksgiving - Well, here is your answer.

Stages Theatre presents 

&quot;Romance/Romance&quot;
(Book and Lyrics by Bary Harman
Music by Keith Herrmann)

This sophisticated musical celebrates courtship, love and fidelity in two very different centuries as lovers discover the timeless truths of romantic relationships.



This musical received 5 Tony nominations.  The New York Times calls it &quot;smart, bubbly and ardent&quot; and the New York Post calls it &quot;a double-dollop of the romantic spirit.&quot;

